  "markup": "Join Chris Carraway DC, and Douglas Johnson ATC, for and insightful review of the interactions of light and tissue and how it can be used clinically, along with a Priority Principle review to guide you through the best practices.\u0026nbsp; Log-in to LTU (www.lasertherapyU.org) at any time in January to view the recorded webinar Nuts \u0026amp; Bolts of Low-Level Laser on the Home Page, jot down your questions, and then join us on Thursday January 28th at 1:00 EST for the LIVE Q\u0026amp;A covering this webinar topic."
}]]></Value>
